author: danj
msg: Addition of WS-RT impl from Mohammad F. in MUSE-86. I had to switch around a few metadata classes and methods in order to get
the proper split of API and impl. The implementation also has an Axis2 dependency that needs to be removed - one part is a
bug that should be reported to Axis2 (but is generic and could go in muse-platform-axis2) and another is part of a SOAP header
processing that should be split out or worked into the isolation layer so OSGi users can use the code.
The build puts these two modules in a 'preview' section, similar to the way our OSGi bundles are organized.
